v1.4.7: add HTMLInputElement.prototype.click() override + consolidated install diagnostics

Path 4: hook input.click() at the prototype layer to catch programmatic clicks
that bypass our document-level click listener. Targets Google Drive Picker /
Sheets Import, which open the OS file dialog without firing showPicker(),
showOpenFilePicker(), or any click DOM event we observe.

actorCreated now emits one consolidated line listing the install status of
all three prototype overrides plus the URL, so a console-clear-then-click
trace still has install info to correlate against subsequent invocations.
